summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2016 K-Z SPORTSMEN. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THERE WAS A SOFT SPOT LOCATED IN THE FLOOR OF THE VEHICLE AND WAS CONCERNED THAT THE STRUCTURE WOULD FAIL. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO THE DEALER WHERE THE TECHNICIAN REINFORCED THE STRUCTURE OF THE FLOOR; HOWEVER, THE FAILURE RECURRED IN MULTIPLE SPOTS. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOTIFIED OF THE FAILURE. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 600. THE VIN WAS NOT AVAILABLE.
